&lt;li&gt;Community Backups de &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;rewindbitcoin.com&#x2F;community-backups&quot;&gt;Rewind Bitcoin&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; utilitzant la xarxa P2P de &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.pears.com&#x2F;guides&#x2F;getting-started&quot;&gt;Pears&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
